I"Ú<p>Today, we are super excited to release a long-awaited feature: Hubs. You can now create your APIs catalogs, directly from Bump.</p>

<p><img src="https://cloud.headwayapp.co/changelogs_images/images/big/000/046/230-4d740fb504ecd138814ef507bb3fc4b256fd2118.png" alt="home-hub.png" /></p>

<p>Highlighted features:</p>
<ul>
  <li>custom domain support</li>
  <li>documentations can be grouped by tag</li>
  <li>default settings at the hub level, applied to all its documentations</li>
  <li>auto-creation of hub documentations from your CI</li>
  <li>and obviously, OpenAPI and AsyncAPI support</li>
</ul>

<p>Hubs are available with our Business plan.  Learn more <a href="https://help.bump.sh/hubs">on our help center</a>.</p>
